Two-faced guy who&rsquo;s only into one-night stands x Beautiful, narcissist &lsquo;Prince&rsquo; whose body is more honest than him.

An average office drone by day and gay-magnet playboy by night, Urakawa Shinobu was living it up as a 'top&rsquo; without anybody knowing about his double life. Or that&rsquo;s how it was supposed to be.

Suddenly, the narcissist Prince of the sales department, Omoteya Hikaru, appears at the gay bar Shinobu frequents. With a half-baked plan to be popular with guys too, Hikaru&rsquo;s invasion of Shinobu&rsquo;s favourite haunt is getting in the way of his game. So to regain his oasis, Shinobu decides to make a move on Hikaru: &ldquo;You&rsquo;ve been waiting, right? For me to hit on you, that is.&rdquo;
